      "abstract": "<jats:p>In the field of Artificial Intelligence, large language models (LLMs) are transforming the landscape of what machines can achieve. These sophisticated models excel at tasks like summarising text, generating human-like content, translating languages, and answering complex questions. However, the computational resources required to run such models can be prohibitive for many individuals and small teams. Let's enter the world of Google Colab.</jats:p>",
